title: Rittal Blue e+ fans and compressor
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/environment/rittal
author: Kuhn & Rueß GmbH <info@kuhn-ruess.de>
license: GPL
distribution: none
description:
 Fan and compressor monitoring of a Rittal Blue e+ cooling unit: internal
 fan, external fan and compressor speed, each in percent with the component
 status from the appliance.

 The running level in percent is emitted as performance data. Components
 reporting status {not available} are not discovered.

item:
 The component: {Fan Internal}, {Fan External} or {Compressor}. When more
 than one Blue e+ unit is connected, the device name is appended in
 parentheses.

inventory:
 One service per fan and compressor of each Blue e+ unit.
